<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>190</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nichuah, nitlak, chaklei, thlanglei, Khrih ah thennak um lo; Dawt
 hawikomhnak pakhat lawng te, Khuazakip a cul ko.

[V2]
 Bawi Khrih chungah miphun 'kip nih, Lungkhat in kan i pum, Sui hri
 bang A-mah riantuan nih, Phunkip mi a kan komh.

[V3]
 Cu ca'h lung le thin komh tuah u, Nan phun zeihmanh siseh, Kan Pa
 riantuanmi vialte cu, U-nau khat kan si dih.

[V4]
 Khrih ah Chak, Thlang an i tong i, Nichuah, Nitlak hna zong. A-mah
 lungthin ngei vialte hi, Pum khat kan si dih cang.</lyrics>
<key>Eb</key>
<title>BAWI KHRIH AH NICHUAH, NITLAK UM LO CH190</title>
</song>